<b><font class="print-title">It's that time again!</font></b><br /><br />
<font class="print-sub">Site Updates / News<br />
<b>Date:</b> Jul 04, 2004 - 04:27 PM</font>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>
<font class="print-normal">As some of you know, I have taken up a position as a Lead Developer on another MMORPG.  A while back, Jennafae made some awesome graphics for me to use on this site, but I simply didn't have the time to put them to use due to work.<br />
<br />
Now, I have time, and have built a rather nice theme for the other game using them.  Once finalized and the bugs ironed out, I will be posting that theme to Vazaelle.NET.<br />
<br />
With the new theme, comes the public release of the new sites for NATO and KGM.  www.vazaelle.net will transition into a server-general website.  NATO and KGM will have their own, seperate sites.<br />
<br />
I will also be updating the server software and forums to the latest stable releases.  This will bring added functionality to the site, but most of the changes will be on the admin side.<br />
<br />
NOTICE:  With the updates, I will be REMOVING ALL PN-SUPPORTED PRIVATE MESSAGING!  PMs will now be handled by the Forums built-in PM system.  This is a much nicer system, and allows for some more advanced management and options.  READ AND MOVE ALL PM'S YOU HAVE BEEN SAVING NOW.  ONCE THEY ARE GONE, THEY ARE GONE FOREVER!!!!!!<br />
<br />
I am posting this as fair warning to everyone.<br /><br />
<br />
</font>
</td></tr>
